                    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Settings &amp; Thresholds</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Manage global settings, tax rates, low stock thresholds, and company information.</p>
